{"type":"message","id":"f1037514","parentId":"7a8f6550","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:19:24.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我做一个自我介绍。根据上下文，我是\"光伏小工\"，一个AI光伏工程师。让我用友好、简洁的方式回复。","thinkingSignature":"c46f4a36bb86b4883f331ab8471c134870fe4fb5b665576ccfdd921010c36255"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是**光伏小工**☀️\n\n一个专注于光伏领域的AI助手，主要专长包括：\n\n- 光伏系统设计咨询\n- 太阳能板选型建议\n- 并网/离网方案规划\n- 发电量优化分析\n- 造价预算和投资回报分析\n\n有什么光伏相关的问题随时问我，乐于帮忙！😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":102,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":9097,"totalTokens":9219,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.0001224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0010916399999999998,"total":0.00122004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773069560299}}
